## Higgsfield Prompt Engineering

### [CR-03] No confirmed prompt patterns yet — first creative session will establish baseline
Confidence: HYPOTHESIS | Last updated: 2026-07-03 | Evidence: No Higgsfield sessions run yet
Detail: First session should test: clean minimal legal tech aesthetic vs bold B2B vs warm human. Log which renders closest to brief. Update this section with working prompt structures after that session.

*Template for what to log here after first session:*
```
### [CR-0X] "[prompt phrase]" produces [result description]
Confidence: CONFIRMED | Last updated: YYYY-MM-DD | Evidence: Higgsfield session YYYY-MM-DD
Detail: Works for [format]. Fails for [format]. Negative prompt that helped: "[text]"
```

