### [CR-04] No format performance data yet — PMax asset labels not assigned
Confidence: HYPOTHESIS | Last updated: 2026-07-03 | Evidence: No campaigns with correct tracking have run yet
Detail: Once Campaign 03 runs and Google assigns asset labels (Good/Best/Low), log which formats (landscape 1200×628, square 1200×1200, portrait 960×1200) perform best for students vs lawyers. This section should fill up within 14 days of Campaign 03 launch.

