## Copy & CTA

### [CR-05] No copy performance data yet — establish baseline in Campaign 03
Confidence: HYPOTHESIS | Last updated: 2026-07-03 | Evidence: No conversion data from campaigns with correct tracking
Detail: Headline angles to test in Campaign 03: benefit-led ("Draft contracts in minutes"), social proof ("Used by 500+ Indian law firms"), fear/urgency ("Missing a deadline costs more than software"). Log which angle gets Best label.

### [CR-06] CTAs approved by council for student audience: "Try free" and "Start today"
Confidence: LIKELY | Last updated: 2026-07-03 | Evidence: CAMPAIGN_BRIEF.md — Aug 2026 draft
Detail: "Book a demo" was considered too high-friction for students. "Try free" aligns with the free-tier entry point. Update to CONFIRMED once an ad with this CTA runs and produces clicks.

