## What Addy does with this file at session end

After every creative session, ask:
1. Did a Higgsfield prompt work well or fail badly? → Update CR-03 or add a new CR entry
2. Did Google assign asset labels since last session? → Update CR-04 or add format entries
3. Did council veto a copy angle or CTA? → Add to CR-05/CR-06
4. Did Transparency Centre research reveal a clear visual pattern? → Update CR-07 or add entry
5. Did a brand constraint cause a problem (logo, UI crop, colours)? → Update CR-01/CR-02

If none of the above → write nothing. Only update when evidence actually changes the model.
